simple thread pool
======

Tt is a simple thread pool based on POSIX thread API.
It is written in C and licensed under the LGPL-2.1 (see COPYING).

Version: 1.02

Homepage:
https://sourceforge.net/projects/thd-pool-linux/

Mail for questions:
- Weirong Yang <boyce.ywr@gmail.com>


INSTALL:
	$ cd build
	$ cmake ..
	$ make 
RUN:
	$ bin/tp_test

History:
1.01

1.02
	fixed some bugs;
	add some features;
	